{"level":"\u001b[32minfo\u001b[39m","message":"\u001b[32mFound therapist: {\"_id\":\"69a53b8f73f38538b6dc3fab\",\"userId\":\"69a53b8e73f38538b6dc3fa9\",\"licenseNumber\":\"696969\",\"licenseState\":\"India\",\"licenseExpiryDate\":\"2027-03-02T07:26:07.002Z\",\"specializations\":[\"Trauma\"],\"certifications\":[],\"bio\":\"Dr. em\\nLicensed Therapist | Mental Health & Emotional Wellness Specialist\\n\\nDr. Dre is a dedicated and compassionate licensed therapist committed to helping individuals achieve emotional balance, personal growth, and lasting mental well-being. With extensive experience in evidence-based therapeutic practices, Dr. Dre specializes in supporting clients through anxiety, depression, stress management, relationship challenges, and life transitions.\\n\\nKnown for a client-centered and empathetic approach, Dr. Dre integrates techniques from Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT), mindfulness-based practices, and solution-focused therapy to create personalized treatment plans tailored to each individual’s unique needs. He provides a safe, confidential, and non-judgmental environment where clients feel empowered to explore their thoughts, emotions, and goals.\\n\\nDr. Dre believes that therapy is a collaborative journey. His mission is to equip clients with practical tools, deeper self-awareness, and resilient coping strategies that promote long-term emotional strength and clarity.\\n\\nWith a strong commitment to ethical practice and continuous professional development, Dr. Dre strives to make mental health care accessible, supportive, and transformative for every individual he works with.\",\"experienceYears\":5,\"languages\":[],\"verificationStatus\":\"VERIFIED\",\"verificationDocuments\":[],\"hourlyRateUSD\":31,\"hourlyRateINR\":2500,\"currency\":\"INR\",\"isAcceptingPatients\":true,\"maxPatientsPerWeek\":20,\"totalReviews\":0,\"totalEarningsUSD\":0,\"totalSessionsCompleted\":0,\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-02T07:26:07.004Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-04T05:5